 processes. Further exploration of the audio\nrevealed many similar events following other major storms, thus they are much\nmore common than previously thought. We therefore highlight the potential of\nsonification and exploratory citizen science in addressing some of the\nchallenges facing ULF wave research.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Nov 2018 10:08:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-08"}
