latory capture is a signature of economic leader dominance,\ne.g. the US. Important roles of political leaders in economics and corruption\nare a signature of the political leader dominance, e.g. China. Ideological\nleaders dominate in theocracies, e.g. Iran. Military leaders dominate in\ndictatorships or where military leaders select leadership, e.g. Egypt.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Nov 2018 14:07:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-08"}
